{"tid":177585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★想一死了之？死後在香港驚人駛費！","createTime":"2017-03-29T03:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T17:23:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"516b12077186fce1568bc8e3d9942f4d66ad7746","tid":177585,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/29/110834_38c2b8c50a0c006b9603eca50b1f0a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F29%2F110834_38c2b8c50a0c006b9603eca50b1f0a07.jpg&h=f78e7436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使是進行同一種宗教儀式，在不同的殯儀館亦相距甚遠。以道教儀式為例，世界殯儀館的道教儀式套餐最貴，職員的口頭報價為約50,000至55,000元。以該館55,000元套餐價作對比，較鑽石山殯儀館道教儀式的27,920元，貴近一倍。<br />\n<br />\n上述每個殯儀套餐所包括的靈堂大小、棺木大小和質素、法事儀式大小不一，需要辦喪事的市民，宜按本身要求，詳細了解不同的套餐收費，決定選擇哪個殯葬儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/article/80917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F80917&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=3065cb6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/article/80917</a>"},{"pid":"dd699a04a8d1bf845373946ee83967cd3f7395cb","tid":177585,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5393edec50e04e03155cabbc310c08c28e8c8574","tid":177585,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"半個月人工"},{"pid":"77b8c9fbed8e43875a23c7910ce5f387df56983d","tid":177585,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇得生前供定？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" clas